cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.SOC, cs.IR, cs.CL 

Reasoning: 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on analyzing real-time prediction problems of hashtags on Twitter, which is a social network platform. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is also a likely category as the paper may discuss the development of algorithms or software tools for predicting bursting hashtags. 
- cs.SOC (Social and Economic Networks) is another possible category as the paper may explore the social and economic implications of bursting hashtags on Twitter. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper may discuss the retrieval and analysis of Twitter data to predict bursting hashtags. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a possible category as the paper may discuss natural language processing techniques used to analyze Twitter data and predict bursting hashtags.
